address2: Flat 314 3rd Floor 28 On Lok Mun Street
longBusinessSummary: CNC Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, primarily provides civil engineering services. It operates through Provision of Civil Engineering Services and Media and Advertising Business segments. The company undertakes waterworks engineering, road works and drainage, and site formation works for the public sector in Hong Kong. It also broadcasts television programs on television channels operated by television broadcasting companies in the Asia-Pacific region. In addition, the company engages in promoting digital marketing activities on overseas video platform in return for advertising and related purposes. CNC Holdings Limited was formerly known as Tsun Yip Holdings Limited and changed its name to CNC Holdings Limited in February 2012. The company was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Fanling, Hong Kong.
